== 出入口 ==
這個站有2個出口：A (西北)、B (西南)。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.beijing.cn/rcpage/ditie/page/100411.shtml |title=北京网交通出行 |access-date=2012-01-16 |archive-date=2012-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124223347/http://www.beijing.cn/rcpage/ditie/page/100411.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=station/>
